# MISC::ACTIVITY_FEED_ADD_INT_TO_CAPTION

## Summary
Adds a int value to the main caption ...using ~1~

## Parameters

## Description
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Does nothing (it's a nullsub). Seems to be PS4 specific.
